<li id="cite_note-salon-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-salon_0-0" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.salon.com/col/shoa/1997/11/13shoa.html" class="external text" title="http://www.salon.com/col/shoa/1997/11/13shoa.html" rel="nofollow">Salon | Ill Humor</a></li>
